&quot;I had direct instructions from Miss Reine not to interfere if such a situation should arise,&quot;<br>
<br>
Finding Kale useless Decker made to stop the conflict but was beaten by the voice that came in through over the intercom.<br>
<br>
&quot;Decker&quot;the voice began, Caron and Matrix instantly fell silent,&quot;Calling Decker, we have news of a soldier seriously hurt and in need of assitance. I repeat, we have news..&quot;<br>
<br>
